data.description: Discover serenity in this stunning home nestled on a lush half-acre lot adorned with majestic trees, on a cul-de-sac.Your two car garage tucked in from a long gated driveway for added peace of mind. Greet your guests in the foyer to begin experiencing the warmth and nostalgia of the home. Living room and loft showcase the abundant natural light and privacy with UV windows screens provide the home. The wood buring fireplace further compliants the custom wood built ins that can be enjoyed in the living room and loft. Kitchen remains to be the hewart of the home with solid wood cabients and granite countertops. With the breakfast nook and dining room giving you options for entertaining. The primary bedroom and retreat completing the main floor. All generously sized  secondary bedrooms are located upstairs with the comfort of recently installed carpet. It's a home that gives you space, privacy and peace of mind all secured with a generator
